[img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/skiller.jpg[/img] Shops(im going to find a different area.. i could use the extra space... :P lul) [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/shops.jpg[/img] This is a pic of home.. idk which one but here is a piece of home :S [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/home3.jpg[/img] This is another pic of home.. idk which one but here is another piece :P! [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/home2.jpg[/img] This is the last pic of home... so here is the last piece :,( here u take it :( [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/home.jpg[/img] Dragon Gfx's all of the dragons have new graphics :P [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/drags.jpg[/img] Last but not least.... Kbd Gfx... remember all the dragons have new gfx's... [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/KBD.jpg[/img]
Well guys I hope i did a great job.. I might add client pics later... but here is mostly server related...The source was coded by me :Taylor (T2kmostkillz on other servers...) Homiescape gets creds for the skillers area like i said... he did a great job. well there u have it i hope you have all enjoyed it as my first Server source coded... bye..Leave a comment if u want..
